TITLE: Basic Usage of Inbox Component in React
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the basic implementation of the Novu Inbox component in a React application. It requires an application identifier and subscriber ID to function properly.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/platform/inbox/react/components/inbox.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { Inbox } from '@novu/react';

function Novu() {
  return (
    <Inbox applicationIdentifier="YOUR_APPLICATION_IDENTIFIER" subscriberId="YOUR_SUBSCRIBER_ID" />
  );
}
```

