TITLE: Triggering WhatsApp Notification with Custom Template (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript code for triggering a WhatsApp notification using Novu with a custom template. It demonstrates how to specify the recipient, payload, and template overrides.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/platform/integrations/chat/(providers)/whats-app.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
novu.trigger('workflow-id', {
  to: {
    subscriberId: 'SUBSCRIBER_ID',
    phone: '+11111111111',
  },
  payload: {},
  overrides: {
    chat: {
      template: {
        name: 'template_name',
        language: {
          code: 'en_US',
        },
      },
    },
  },
});
```

