TITLE: Custom Notification Rendering in Inbox Component
DESCRIPTION: Example of completely customizing the look of notification items using the renderNotification prop. This allows for full control over how each notification is displayed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/platform/inbox/react/components/inbox.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { Inbox } from '@novu/react';

function Novu() {
  return (
    <Inbox
      applicationIdentifier="YOUR_APPLICATION_IDENTIFIER"
      subscriberId="YOUR_SUBSCRIBER_ID"
      renderNotification={(notification) => (
        <div>
          <h3>{notification.subject}</h3>
          <p>{notification.body}</p>
        </div>
      )}
    />
