TITLE: Advanced Digest Event Processing with Component Rendering
DESCRIPTION: Shows advanced usage of digest events including mapping event data to custom activities and rendering a React component for email content. Implements hourly digest with custom activity processing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/framework/typescript/steps/digest.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { ActivityDigestEmail } from './ActivityDigestEmail';

const { events } = await step.digest('activity-digest', async () => {
  return {
    amount: 1,
    unit: 'hours',
  };
});

await step.email('digest-notification', async () => {
  const activities = events.map((event) => ({
    type: event.payload.type,
    user: event.payload.userName,
    action: event.payload.action,
  }));

  return {
    subject: `Activity Summary (${events.length} updates)`,
    body: render(<ActivityDigestEmail activities={activities} />),
  };
});
```

