TITLE: Accessing and Processing Digested Events in TSX
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to access the array of digested events and use them in subsequent workflow steps. It demonstrates retrieving event count and sending a summary email after collecting events for 3 days.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/framework/digest.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const { events } = await step.digest('digest-3-days', async () => {
  return {
    unit: 'days', // 'seconds' | 'minutes' | 'hours' | 'days' | 'weeks' | 'months'
    amount: 3, // the number of units to digest events for
  };
});

await step.email('send-email', async () => {
  const eventCount = events.length;

  return {
    subject: 'Digest Email',
    body: `You have ${eventCount} new events`,
  };
});
```

