TITLE: Creating a Basic Notification Workflow in TypeScript with Novu Framework
DESCRIPTION: A simple example of a workflow that sends an email after a one-day delay. It demonstrates the basic structure of a Novu workflow including a delay Action step and an email Channel step.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/framework/introduction.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { workflow } from '@novu/framework';

workflow('sample-workflow', async (step) => {
  await step.delay('delay', async () => {
    return {
      unit: 'days',
      amount: 1,
    };
  });

  await step.email('email-step', async () => {
    return {
      subject: 'Welcome to Novu',
      body: 'Hello, welcome to Novu!',
    };
  });
});
```

