TITLE: Novu SDK Usage in EU Region
DESCRIPTION: Show how to use the Novu SDK to trigger a notification event in the EU region. Includes setting up the Novu client with the EU server URL and sending a trigger event with subscriber details and payload.
SOURCE: https://github.com/novuhq/docs/blob/main/content/docs/platform/sdks/server/python.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
import novu_py
from novu_py import Novu
import os

with Novu(
server_url="https://eu.api.novu.co",
secret_key=os.getenv("NOVU_SECRET_KEY", ""),
) as novu:

    res = novu.trigger(trigger_event_request_dto=novu_py.TriggerEventRequestDto(
        workflow_id="workflow_identifier",
        to={
            "subscriber_id": "subscriber_unique_identifier",
        },
        payload={
            "comment_id": "string",
            "post": {
                "text": "string",
            },
        },
        overrides={
          "email": {
            "bcc": "no-reply@novu.co"
          }
        },
    ))

    # Handle response
    print(res)
```

